        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Pitch-Center </text><image src="Red-14-3.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image> is the path, or locus, of the center of a circular <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Cam-Follower</text> relative to the <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Cam-Part</text>, throughout a <text style="font-weight:normal;">machine-cycle. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text style="font-weight:normal;">When the shape of the Cam-Follower</text><text style="font-weight:bold;">&#32;</text>is not circular, the <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Pitch-Curve</text> has no useful meaning. </para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
